      <entry>
       <para>
        <literal>ifcfg: <replaceable>NETWORK_CONFIGURATION</replaceable></literal>
       </para>
      </entry>
      <entry>
       <para>
        设置并启动网络。有关更多信息，请参见<xref linkend="ay-adv-network"/>。
       </para>
      </entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry>
       <para>
        <literal>insmod: <replaceable>MODULE</replaceable></literal>
       </para>
      </entry>
      <entry>
       <para>
        装载 <replaceable>MODULE</replaceable>。
       </para>
      </entry>
     </row>
     <row>
      <entry>
       <para>
        <literal>install: <replaceable>URL</replaceable></literal>
       </para>
      </entry>
      <entry>
       <para>
        从 <replaceable>URL</replaceable> 指定的软件源安装。有关 <replaceable>URL</replaceable> 的语法，请参见 <link xlink:href="https://en.opensuse.org/SDB:Linuxrc#url_descr"/>。
       </para>
      </entry>
